Tyler Hoechlin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tyler_Hoechlin 0 Tyler Lee Hoechlin (; September 11, 1987) is an American actor. He got his big break starring as Michael Sullivan Jr. in the 2002 film Road to Perdition. On television he is known for playing the role of Martin Brewer on 7th Heaven, Derek Hale on Teen Wolf, and Superman on Supergirl. Tyler_Lee_Hoechlin ( ; September_11_,_1987 ) is an_American_actor .
